column2:
fishnet %>%
    mutate(
      local_i = local_moran[, 1],
      p_value = local_moran[, 5],
      is_significant = p_value < 0.05,
      
      moran_class = case_when(
        !is_significant ~ "Not Significant",
        local_i > 0 & fishnet[["streetLights_allOut"]] > mean_val ~ "High-High",
        local_i > 0 & fishnet[["streetLights_allOut"]] <= mean_val ~ "Low-Low",
        local_i < 0 & fishnet[["streetLights_allOut"]] > mean_val ~ "High-Low",
        local_i < 0 & fishnet[["streetLights_allOut"]] <= mean_val ~ "Low-High",
        TRUE ~ "Not Significant"
      )
    )
Simple feature collection with 2458 features and 9 fields
